pageContext.claim: “We were supposed to be there for 30 days - That was 10 years ago. When these pundit fools who have called the Middle East wrong for 20 years ask what we are getting out of the deal, I simply say, THE OIL, AND WE ARE BRINGING OUR SOLDIERS BACK HOME, ISIS SECURED!”
pageContext.analysis: There was no end date when President Obama sent the first deployment of 50 special ops forces to Syria in October 2015. Trump has at various times suggested an end date of four months or even as short as 30 days.
